EL
v.
SUMMIT CTY. COURT OF COMMON PLEAS. 2017-1358 Supreme Court of Ohio. March 14, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

O'Connor, C.J., and O'Donnell, Kennedy, French, Fischer, DeWine, and DeGenaro, JJ., concur.

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

In Mandamus. On respondents' motions to dismiss. Motions granted. Cause dismissed. On relator's motion to vacate eviction and motion for fiduciary request/picture evidence supporting request. Motions denied as moot.
